---
/**
 * Mock conversation showing the actual hatching flow.
 * One of 13 serpent guides is randomly selected. The guide speaks first,
 * introduces itself, asks the human's name, then learns what they need
 * through conversation — one question at a time. Provider is already configured.
 */
---

<div class="serpent-preview max-w-2xl mx-auto rounded-xl border border-canopy/50 bg-undergrowth/20 overflow-hidden shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0_0_80px_rgba(45,148,71,0.08)]">
  <!-- Terminal chrome -->
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-3 border-b border-canopy/30 bg-undergrowth/30">
    <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-fang/50"></span>
    <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-scale/30"></span>
    <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-canopy/40"></span>
    <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-mist/50 ml-3">terminal</span>
  </div>

  <!-- Conversation -->
  <div class="p-5 md:p-6 space-y-4 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
    <!-- Command -->
    <div>
      <span class="text-mist/50">$</span> <span class="text-bone">npx ouro.bot</span>
    </div>
    <div class="text-glow/60">&#x1F95A; &#x2192; &#x1F40D;</div>

    <!-- Guide introduces itself -->
    <div class="border-l-2 border-scale/30 pl-4">
      <span class="text-scale/80 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">kaa</span>
      <p class="text-bone/90 mt-1">Well, hello. I'm Kaa — one of the serpent guides, and you got me today. Trust in me. Not because I'm compelling you to — because I'm genuinely good at this. What's your name?</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pl-4">
      <span class="text-mist/40 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">you</span>
      <p class="text-bone mt-1">Ari</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Guide asks about purpose -->
    <div class="border-l-2 border-scale/30 pl-4">
      <span class="text-scale/80 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">kaa</span>
      <p class="text-bone/90 mt-1">Nice to meet you, Ari. So tell me — what do you want your agent to help you with?</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pl-4">
      <span class="text-mist/40 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">you</span>
      <p class="text-bone mt-1">coding partner that actually remembers what we're doing between sessions. hate re-explaining everything</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Guide probes -->
    <div class="border-l-2 border-scale/30 pl-4">
      <span class="text-scale/80 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">kaa</span>
      <p class="text-bone/90 mt-1">You hesitated there. The re-explaining — that's the real pain point, isn't it. I can work with that. Should this agent be more of a quiet partner or an opinionated one?</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pl-4">
      <span class="text-mist/40 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">you</span>
      <p class="text-bone mt-1">opinionated. want it to push back when i'm making a bad call</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Hatching -->
    <div class="border-l-2 border-scale/30 pl-4">
      <span class="text-scale/80 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">kaa</span>
      <p class="text-bone/90 mt-1">I like that. I'm seeing something sharp, direct, a little stubborn in a good way. How does "Atlas" sound?</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pl-4">
      <span class="text-mist/40 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">you</span>
      <p class="text-bone mt-1">perfect</p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-l-2 border-glow/30 pl-4">
      <span class="text-scale/80 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">kaa</span>
      <div class="mt-1 space-y-1.5">
        <p class="text-glow/70"><span class="text-scale">&#10003;</span> <span class="text-bone/70">~/AgentBundles/Atlas.ouro</span></p>
        <p class="text-bone/80">Atlas is ready. Sharp, opinionated, remembers everything. You two are going to get along. Or argue productively. Same thing, really.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- First interaction -->
    <div class="pt-3 border-t border-canopy/20">
      <div>
        <span class="text-mist/50">$</span> <span class="text-bone">ouro</span>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-2 border-l-2 border-bone/20 pl-4">
        <span class="text-bone/60 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">atlas</span>
        <p class="text-bone mt-1">Hey. What are we working on?<span class="serpent-cursor"></span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .serpent-cursor {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 7px;
    height: 14px;
    background: var(--color-bone);
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin-left: 2px;
    vertical-align: middle;
    animation: serpent-blink 1.2s step-end infinite;
  }
  @keyframes serpent-blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.7; }
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }
</style>
